Is this a good move? Yes, it is. In the first look, it might be proceed as 23...Bxd4 24.Bxd4+ Rf6 25.Bxf6+ Qxf6 where the material is equal for both sides. Can you see the BEST reply there? After 23...Bxd4, it is a wonderful mate in 7. But the game was ended in 6 moves.
